                                          {
                                            "nodeId": 20,
                                            "accessibilityText": "I\u2019m a Senior Product Manager at Luciq (formerly Instabug), a B2B enterprise SaaS platform specializing in mobile observability, based in Cairo, Egypt. Since joining in September 2022, I\u2019ve grown from Associate PM to Senior PM, building my product career entirely within the mobile observability and developer tooling space.\r\n\r\nToday, I lead a portfolio that spans Bug Reporting, Session Replay, and Surveys, working alongside a team of engineers to deliver tools that help mobile teams ship better software. I\u2019ve shipped two AI-powered features at Luciq, AI Bug Grouping and AI Session Insights, and led Session Replay to product-market fit in under twelve months, contributing to meaningful enterprise customer growth.\r\nI\u2019m particularly interested in the intersection of AI and product development, both as a product builder shipping AI features to customers, and as a practitioner using tools like Claude, Cursor, and MCP integrations to reshape how product managers work day to day. ",
